== Frame statement ==

This wiki treats psionics — together with the closely related fields of [[Electrogravitics|electrogravitics]], [[Zero-Point_Energy|zero-point energy]], extra-dimensional physics, [[Anomalous_Cognition|anomalous cognition]], and contact phenomena — as ''real science'' whose public face has been deliberately limited. The aim of the [[Psionics]] cluster of the FusionGirl wiki is to recover that science, present its equations and experiments cleanly, and provide an honest map for readers from any background.

